The paper proposes a novel online multiple-output regression method for streaming data, which is a machine learning technique. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The method also involves statistical variables and a forgetting factor, which are related to data analysis and information theory, respectively. Therefore, it may also belong to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Statistics (cs.ST), and Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-categories.
